nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Create a luxurious beauty portrait where the woman holds a single bottle of Tom Ford Lost Cherry perfume in one hand near her face. Use the face, platinum hairstyle, red lipstick, and red halter dress from the Marilyn Monroe-inspired character image. Maintain her classic glamour and confident expression.

Match the pose and hand orientation from the reference image (bottom right), but only one hand should be visible, holding the perfume. Position the Tom Ford Lost Cherry bottle clearly in the shot, upright and readable, scaled to look naturally held. Use the exact bottle design: deep cherry red glass, clean label, and squared cap.

Set the background to the glossy red tile texture from the provided background image. Ensure the lighting complements the tiles’ reflective surfaces and enhances the red tones in both the dress and perfume bottle.
